Name: riboplot
Version: 0.2.1
Summary: Plot read counts of RiboSeq data from BAM format alignment files
Home-page: https://github.com/vimalkumarvelayudhan/riboplot
Author: Vimalkumar Velayudhan
Author-email: vimalkumarvelayudhan@gmail.com
